* Schema\nEnforcement
** What it is
***_ Delta Lake built-in validation
***_ Compares incoming vs target types
***_ Applied on every write
** Rules
***_ Columns must exist in table
***_ Types must match or be castable
***_ Safe casts attempted automatically
** Behavior
*** Success
****_ '100' cast to INT succeeds
****_ Compatible types promoted
*** Failure
****_ 'fifty' to INT fails
****_ Write operation rejected
** First Line of Defense
***_ Catches type mismatches early
***_ No extra code required
***_ Use explicit casting for more control
@endmindmap
